{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/append\"><code>append()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/forEach\"><code>forEach()</code></a></li><li><em><code>get()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/keys\"><code>keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/sort\"><code>sort()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>URL API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a> インターフェースの <strong><code>get()</code></strong> メソッドは、指定された検索パラメーターに関連付けられた最初の値を返します。</span></p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>注:</strong> この機能は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 内で利用可能です</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">URLSearchParams.get(<em>name</em>)</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"パラメーター","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\">name</dt>\n <dd>返すパラメーターの名前。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>指定された検索パラメーターが見つかった場合、<a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>。 それ以外の場合、<strong><code>null</code></strong>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>ページの URL が <code>https://example.com/?name=Jonathan&amp;age=18</code> の場合、次を使用して 'name' および 'age' のパラメーターを解析できます。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"default prettyprint prettyprinted notranslate\"><code>let params = new URLSearchParams(document.location.search.substring(1));\nlet name = params.get(\"name\")<span class=\"kwd\">; // 文字列 \"Jonathan\" です。\n</span>let age = parseInt(params.get(\"age\"), 10<span class=\"kwd\">); // 数値 18 です。</span></code>\n</pre>\n\n<p>クエリー文字列に存在しないパラメーターを要求すると、<strong><code>null</code></strong> が返されます。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>let address = params.get(\"address\"); // null</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlsearchparams-get\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">URL<br><small lang=\"ja\">get() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.URLSearchParams.get","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"URLSearchParams インターフェースの get() メソッドは、指定された検索パラメーターに関連付けられた最初の値を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/urlsearchparams/get","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/urlsearchparams/get/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams","title":"URLSearchParams"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get","title":"URLSearchParams.get()"}],"pageTitle":"URLSearchParams.get() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}